<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Classigoo - Your OTP for Authentication</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
      }
      .warning {
        color: #721c24;
        background-color: #f8d7da;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h2>Hi {{name}},</h2>

      <p>We have received a one-time password generation request from your email
        address. Please use the code below to complete your authentication.</p>

      <p><strong>Your code is valid for the next 5 minutes.</strong></p>

      <div class='otp-code'>
        {{code}}
      </div>

      <div class='warning'>
        If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email. For your
        security, you can login to the Classigoo app and visit the security
        center to monitor logged-in users.
      </div>

      <p>For further help, please contact our support department.</p>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Regards,<br />Team Classigoo</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>